{
  "chapter": 52,
  "chapter_summary": "第五十二章：风雨前夕。夜深寒风中，裴珏、那飞虹、袁泸珍在庭园中听到暗处神秘人的冷笑警告，裴珏追寻未果。那飞虹放下屠刀后感叹为善之乐，三人感受到善良人性的温暖。与此同时，汉口城内飞龙镖局地盘接连发生命案，\"战神手\"已开始行动，城中陷入混乱。\"龙形八掌\"檀明携女儿檀文琪连夜赶来，与东方五兄弟会面，重提檀文琪与东方震的婚事。檀明急于将女儿许配出去，以应对飞龙镖局面临的劲敌。东方湖当面质问檀明与十余年前无头公案的关系，檀明以狂笑掩饰。正当婚事将定时，柳辉送来三只红木拜盒——内装飞龙镖局三名得力镖师的人头，檀明大惊失色。东方震突然不知去向，黎明将至，风雨将临。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "裴珏等三人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "暗处神秘人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "知过能改，尚属可教，你若妄施毒计，此刻还有命么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师傅！老前辈……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师傅！老前辈……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "放下屠刀，立地成佛，小弟真该恭喜那兄……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_lu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "袁泸珍",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "从今以后，想必你睡觉也可睡得安稳些了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "那飞虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到为善毕竟比作恶愉快得多！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "街人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "战神手已开始行动了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "飞龙传令者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "凡属飞龙旗下兄弟，一齐聚集到长江渡头，不得分散！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "路人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "龙形八掌来了！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_tan_wen_qi",
      "text": "琪儿，下来。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "speaker_name": "东方铁",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "speaker_name": "东方铁",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "檀大叔怎地乘夜赶来了？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "text": "昨日已应在此等候贤侄们大驾，一步来迟，却叫你们无端受到了许多狂徒的胡言乱语。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "speaker_name": "东方铁",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "檀大叔的消息倒灵通的很。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "年前承蒙贤侄们不弃，而有招亲之意，但老夫那时只觉小女年纪太轻，又恐高攀不上，是以未敢仓促决定。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但自从'浪莽山庄'以后，小女得蒙震世兄大力维护之后，想不到她对震世兄……唉，竟已动了痴心。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "speaker_name": "东方铁",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "三弟当真有福了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老夫一生闯荡江湖，只得此女，是以……唉！既是她心里愿意，老夫也只得厚颜来向世兄们重提旧议。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只是……唉，老夫门户太低，不知是否高攀得上？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "speaker_name": "东方铁",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "檀大叔名满天下，领袖武林，十年来江湖英雄，从未有一人之声名能与檀大叔相埒。檀大叔若是再说门户太低，小侄们便不知如何是好了！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "text": "贤侄过誉了……如此说来，不知震世兄身边可曾带得有文定之物？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "speaker_name": "东方铁",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "不过……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "text": "什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "speaker_name": "东方铁",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "檀大叔不嫌今夜仓促了些？这是三弟终身之事，我兄弟无论如何也该为他做得郑重些才是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "text": "此……事……说……来……虽然不错，但此刻事态非常，凡事只好从权，好在你我俱是武林中人，也不必来拘这些虚礼……哈哈，你说是么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_jiang",
      "speaker_name": "东方江",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "事态非常？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不瞒贤侄们说，我'飞龙镖局'，今日实已遇着了劲敌，老夫只此一女，总要她先有了归宿，才能安心。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "speaker_name": "东方铁",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "檀大叔爱女心切，此话也是道理。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_hu",
      "speaker_name": "东方湖",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "近日听得武林传言，说是檀大叔与十余年前那一段无头公案有些关系，不知此事是真是假？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "草莽匹夫的恶意中伤，老夫从未放在心上，贤侄们却信以为真了么？",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "speaker_name": "东方铁",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_hu",
      "text": "檀大叔游走江湖，少不得要结下许多仇家，五弟，你怎能——",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_hu",
      "text": "湖世兄热血直肠，正是我少年时的心性，我怎会怪他？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "text": "铁世兄，长兄为父，古有名训，今日之事，若是铁世兄一口承担下来．想必老爷子……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hui",
      "speaker_name": "柳辉",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "外面有人送来三匣礼物，不知总镖头可要看上一看？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_jiang",
      "speaker_name": "东方江",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "如有不便，檀大叔自管出去便是。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_liu_hui",
      "text": "在贤侄们面前，还有什么不方便的事！柳兄！便请你将那三匣礼物取来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hui",
      "speaker_name": "柳辉",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "但……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_liu_hui",
      "text": "听到了么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_hu",
      "speaker_name": "东方湖",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "不知檀大叔究竟有什么可喜可赞之事，如此深夜，还有人送礼过来？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_liu_hui",
      "text": "送礼的人哪里去了？老夫倒要好好酬谢他一番。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hui",
      "speaker_name": "柳辉",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "方才只听到门外一阵响动，开门一看，这三匣东西已放在门前的石阶上，送礼的人却早已走了。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "见不得人的鼠辈！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_jian",
      "speaker_name": "东方剑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三弟呢？哪里去了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_zhen",
      "text": "震世兄，东方震……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    }
